{"tid":1014631,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇人係香港報外國工又成功去到外國做？","createTime":"2019-02-09T11:08:23.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-09T11:22:03.000Z","uid":122016,"like":0,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"b397d99c8f795faa422ca948b2dc7e12c613c668","tid":1014631,"uid":122016,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-09T11:08:23.000Z","msg":"可唔可以分享一下你地嘅經歷，同埋去左邊到做邊行<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n一直想去外國做野，但暫時遇到幾個問題<br />\n<br />\n1.我見好多工尤其係啲 graduate program 會要求去當地assessment Centre(第一關）<br />\n<br />\n2.好多都要求master 或者 2:1,自己成績比較差得 2:2<br />\n<br />\n3.好多公司填學歷只有本地大學，外國只能填 others, 會唔會塭啲非 graduate program 嘅工比較好？始終感覺上啲 graduate program 會想請本地畢業生多<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n如果我1.儲定一舊錢直接飛去嗰邊定居搵工好啲定 2.係嗰邊補個master再搵工 或者 3.繼續係香港揾英國工直到揾到(如果有 final round 會飛過去in）<br />\n<br />\n自己做工程，畢業做左年半到，Hku grad  揸英國護照"},{"pid":"3c40067bfc73505d96902744bf9adf23bd2a2c0f","tid":1014631,"uid":155818,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-09T11:11:38.000Z","msg":"你已經跑嬴好多人<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"421dcba66380f47bcd87252f9ec9c6795dc50ef1","tid":1014631,"uid":161374,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-02-09T11:14:10.000Z","msg":"點都好，做過野先好master！"},{"pid":"5cc627b2f46449a798c4ee0240acc5c520ce772e","tid":1014631,"uid":213217,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"421dcba66380f47bcd87252f9ec9c6795dc50ef1","tid":1014631,"uid":161374,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-02-09T11:14:10.000Z","msg":"點都好，做過野先好master！"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-09T11:15:36.000Z","msg":"未必。表組hku engine grad.  去澳洲讀完master, phd先做野。直做中高層，準備申請移民。"},{"pid":"9697170578da3f25ab3e4a143721074214321325","tid":1014631,"uid":213217,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5cc627b2f46449a798c4ee0240acc5c520ce772e","tid":1014631,"uid":213217,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"421dcba66380f47bcd87252f9ec9c6795dc50ef1","tid":1014631,"uid":161374,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score"